Ranger Help for: gaia's touch
===============================

SYNTAX:      rtouch <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   8
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to channel Gaia's restorative power through
touch, healing the wounds of a target. The amount of hit points healed
depends on the Ranger's wisdom, guild level, and connection to Gaia.
The Ranger may use this skill on themselves or on an ally. Healing is
more effective in the Ranger's primary terrain, where the connection
to the land is strongest.
